"title": "5636: work, and rest",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5636: work, and rest",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>In creation, God has established a pattern of work and rest that is to be a model for believers.</p>\n<h2>Work and rest built into creation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:11\">EXO 20:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:1-Gen2:3\">GEN 2:1–2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:19-Ps104:23\">PSA 104:19–104:23</a></p>\n<h2>The pattern of work and rest confirmed in the OT</h2>\n<h3>By Sabbath observance</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:10\">EXO 20:10</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:14\">DEU 5:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:3\">LEV 23:3</a></p>\n<h3>By observing holy festivals</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:16\">EXO 12:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:29\">LEV 16:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:6-Lev23:8\">LEV 23:6–23:8</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num28:17-Num28:18\">NUM 28:17–28:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:28-Lev23:31\">LEV 23:28–23:31</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num29:7\">NUM 29:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:35-Lev23:36\">LEV 23:35–23:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:39\">LEV 23:39</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num29:12\">NUM 29:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth9:17-Esth9:19\">EST 9:17–9:19</a></p>\n<h2>Work and rest in the ministry of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:30-Mark6:32\">MRK 6:30–6:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:6\">JHN 4:6</a></p>\n<h2>Wisdom needed to balance work and rest</h2>\n<h3>To avoid idleness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:9-Prov6:11\">PRO 6:9–6:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:4-Prov10:5\">PRO 10:4–10:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:23\">PRO 14:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:13\">PRO 20:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:30-Prov24:34\">PRO 24:30–24:34</a></p>\n<h3>To avoid overwork</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod18:13-Exod18:24\">EXO 18:13–18:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps127:2\">PSA 127:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:38-Luke10:42\">LUK 10:38–10:42</a></p>\n<h2>Work and rest are both potential means of glorifying God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:31\">1CO 10:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:24\">ECC 2:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:17\">COL 3:17</a></p>\n<h2>Work and rest will be perfectly fulfilled in heaven</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:13\">REV 14:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:3\">REV 22:3</a></strong></p>",
